At that moment, my aunt had just given me a flute of champagne, and I cautioned my friend to be cautious. However, friends don't always fully consider their actions. With a gentle push from her, I found myself plunging into the water. Coming up for air, I was met with her laughter and earnest apologies. My exquisite gown was completely spoiled. My cousin light-heartedly remarked on how I nearly made a splash on the wedding cake.
